                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1110" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0100</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9154 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">未来，何去何从？——A证券公司C营业部员工流失的风波</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Where Is The Future—The Confusion of Personnel Drain in A Securities Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">何波，王朝全等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西南科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A证券公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">20 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">员工流失；A证券公司C营业部；人力资源；2013百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Staff turnover; A securities company C saling-department;Enterprise development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了A证券公司C营业部三类核心员工流失的具体过程。2011年前尽管证券行业的人才流失现象严重，A证券公司公司C营业部的员工流失率远远低于同行业水平，然而随着行业环境的变化和公司的扩张，竞争加剧、人心浮躁、业绩下降等问题开始暴露出来。为了应对这一系列挑战C营业部开始推行精细化管理，没想到这些举措不但没能调动起大家的积极性，反而引发更多的不满情绪，公司开始掀起了离职潮。本案例按照时间顺序依次描述了C营业部员工流失的具体现状，力求寻找到员工流失的主要原因，从而引导对如何解决员工流失问题的进一步思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The era of knowledge economy, talents become the new scarce resources more than financial capital,and also become the fundamental power for reality and the future economic development. However, some industry or some enterprise employees’ turnover rate is high, especially in the securities industry. Some securities company personnel turnover rate reaches 50%, talent annualised turnover amounted to 90%, the staff’s frequently job-hopping not only affects the stability of the enterprise, but also take away the enterprise customers or the technical secrets, make the enterprise inestimable losses. This case describes the A securities Company C saling-department’s situation of staffs loss, and strive to look for the root of employee turnover, put forward the  specific measures to solve this problem.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2012</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《组织行为学》、《管理学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">激励</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013-03</td>
                            </tr>
